OL,5, Stricter limits are needed on levels of
OL,6, 'forever chemicals' in UK drinking     
OL,7, water which are potentially harmful to 
OL,8, human health, experts have warned.     
OL,10,FIn high doses these pollutants, known  
OL,11,Fas PFAS, have been linked to serious   
OL,12,Fhealth concerns including cancer and   
OL,13,Ffertility issues.                      
OL,15,FThe Royal Society of Chemistry urged   
OL,16,Fthe government to toughen regulations  
OL,17,Fin line with other countries.          
OL,19,FThe government said current safety     
OL,20,Fstandards were "exceptionally high".   
